I"1<p>The <code>london_underground</code> sensor will display the status of London underground lines, as well as the Overground, DLR and Tfl rail.</p>
<pre><code class="language-yaml"># Example configuration.yaml entry
sensor:
  - platform: london_underground
    line:
      - Bakerloo
      - Central
      - Circle
      - District
      - DLR
      - Hammersmith &amp; City
      - Jubilee
      - London Overground
      - Metropolitan
      - Northern
      - Piccadilly
      - TfL Rail
      - Victoria
      - Waterloo &amp; City
</code></pre>
